Through the Sad Bots Metaverse, our long term goal is to create a positive safe space for the community to look after their mental health & well-being.

By promoting love, freedom of self, and belonging, we can build a series of meaningful experiences and memories together.

🧵/3

The space of NFTs often comes with unique stress factors, such as FOMO, FUD and imposter syndrome. Oftentimes, it is difficult for those outside to empathise and understand this stress, given the culture and subject of NFTs is still new and frequently under wide scrutiny.
